    "description": "Mikuni Corporation manufactures and sells automobile related products in Japan and internationally. The company's automobiles products include electronic controlled throttle bodies, plastic intake manifolds, variable valve timing systems, electric oil and vacuum pumps, electronic exhaust valves, cooling water control valves, and active pedals; electronic control throttle body, throttle body, electronic control throttle body, intake module, intake module for outboard engines, engine ECU, variable valve timing and oil control, trochoid oil pump, water pump, plastic fuel pump, secondary air valve, TMR carburetors for motorcycles for motorcycles; and intake module for personal water crafts; valve, variable valve timing and oil control valve for outboard engines. It also provides gas and water control devices, water control devices, accessory parts for fuel cells, and humidifiers; nursing equipment and consumer products; aircraft parts and maintenance materials; turf-care equipment. In addition, the company offers heaters, engine preheaters, fuel injection systems and related devices, gas safety devices, lawn mowers, welfare equipment and services, and real estate management and leasing services. The company was formerly known as Mikuni Kogyo Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Mikuni Corporation in 1991. Mikuni Corporation was founded in 1923 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
